<p><span style="font-size: 24px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 34.2856px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(217, 216, 216); line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); line-height: 2em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 57px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">12月13日是国家的公祭日，也是震惊世界的南京大屠杀惨案的发生日。为了警示同学们铭记历史的屈辱，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 2em; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 57px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; outline: none 0px !important;">弘扬爱国之情、 砥砺强国之志</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(217, 216, 216); line-height: 2em; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 57px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">、激荡信仰力量、勇担历史使命、实践报国之行，追忆</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(217, 216, 216); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 34px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 57px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">逝者，缅怀英雄。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 57px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">经济管理学院<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 34px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">全体师生于2023年12月13日在经济管理学院大厅举办以“缅怀先烈，铭记历史”为主题的国家公祭日系列缅怀教育活动。</span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 34.2856px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(217, 216, 216); line-height: 2em; font-size: 24px; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 34px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(217, 216, 216); font-size: 14px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); line-height: 2em; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; outline: none 0px !important;">同学们面对鲜红的谨言，</span><span style="max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 34px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(217, 216, 216); font-size: 14px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); line-height: 2em; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; outline: none 0px !important;">纷纷庄重地签下自己的名字，一个个名字都是一颗颗热忱的心，彰显了同学们的拳拳爱国之心，既是对遇难者的缅怀，也是对青年责任的一份担当。</span></span></p><p><span style="max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 34px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(217, 216, 216); font-size: 14px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); line-height: 2em; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; outline: none 0px !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240113/1705116428409062212.jpg" title="1705116428409062212.jpg" alt="43205da5d70ad798f2f979fb4e5d9371.jpg" width="1078" height="418" style="width: 1078px; height: 418px;"/></span></p>